Nationality:   Serbian-American
Field:         Engineering
Known For:     AC electricity, induction motor
Contribution:  Alternating current power systems; Tesla coil; radio foundation
Quote:         "The present is theirs; the future is mine."

Name:          Isaac Newton
Lived:         1643 - 1727
Nationality:   English
Field:         Physics/Math
Known For:     Laws of Motion, Gravity
Contribution:  Principia Mathematica; invented calculus; explained planetary motion
Quote:         "If I have seen further, it is by standing on the shoulders of giants."

Name:          Socrates
Lived:         470 - -399
Nationality:   Greek
Field:         Philosophy
Known For:     Socratic method
Contribution:  Father of Western philosophy; sentenced to death; documented by Plato
Quote:         "The only true wisdom is knowing you know nothing."

